We are now accepting applications for a small studio!<br>
<br>
Welcome to Greenbriar Village Apartments!<br>
<br>
Greenbriar Village is tucked away on the hillside at the end of Slavin Rd, giving you the best of both city living and the wonderful lush green Oregon is known for. You will be just five minutes south of downtown Portland, and in just minutes you can be at the ease of public transportation. Take the aerial tram to work at OHSU or hop on I-5 and have an easy commute to Lewis &amp; Clark College or PCC's Sylvania campus. Greenbriar is surrounded by beautiful trees with views overlooking Johns Landing, the serene Willamette River, and even Mt. Hood!! It really is the best of both worlds!<br>
<br>
FEATURED: Unit 132, small studio<br>
• Rent: $1,195.00/Month<br>
• Available: Now!!<br>
<br>
• Screening Fee: $20.00 per applicant age 18 and older<br>
• Security Deposit: Equal to one month's rent<br>
• Utilities are tenant-responsibility<br>
<br>
Unit Features:<br>
• Bottom Floor / First Level Apartment Studio<br>
• Vinyl Flooring throughout<br>
• Ceiling Fan in the Living Room<br>
• Electric Oven, Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Garbage Disposal in kitchen<br>
